I""<p>First, create ssh key and copy public key to Github</p>
<hr />

<h3 id="clone-repository-to-local">Clone repository to local</h3>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>rm -rf prevGitDir
git clone repositoryPathUsingSSH
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Upon new modification</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git commit -am 'message'
git push
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Change to another remote branch</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git fetch
git checkout newBranch
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Regular check</p>
<pre><code class="language-angular2html">git status
git branch
</code></pre>

